</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-43_ pf-text-1">Resuscitation Council UK Guidelines and British Heart Foundation recommendations emphasize the importance of AED availability in public spaces and workplaces.


































</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-45_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-46_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-47_ pf-heading-1-h3">Best practices
