</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-52_ pf-text-1"><strong>Maintenance</strong> - Regular checks and maintenance of the AED unit as per the manufacturer's guidelines ensure readiness for an emergency.


































